The paper deals with computer-aided diagnosis systems for classification of skin lesions using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of transfer learning and domain-specific augmentations also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of dermoscopy images, which are a type of medical imaging, suggesting a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
